text: Vianney Marlen Trejo Delgadillo (born 2 August 1994) is a Mexican Paralympic swimmer who competes in international level events. She was born with a right arm malformation and underdeveloped legs. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City Category:Paralympic swimmers of Mexico Category:Mexican female swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Paralympics Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming Championships
